# --- Local dev: FastAPI (phase6) ---
# Origin for JSON API used by Next.js rewrites (/api/backend → BACKEND_URL).
# Must be uvicorn/FastAPI, not Streamlit (Streamlit does not serve /ui-api/*).
BACKEND_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8010

# --- Optional: link to deployed Streamlit UI (nav opens new tab when set) ---
# NEXT_PUBLIC_STREAMLIT_APP_URL=https://zomatorecommendations.streamlit.app

# --- Vercel (Import Git repo → New Project) ---
# • Root Directory: frontend-next
# • Environment variables (Production + Preview):
#     BACKEND_URL = https://<your-fastapi-host>     ← required for Home / History / Metrics API calls
#     NEXT_PUBLIC_STREAMLIT_APP_URL = https://zomatorecommendations.streamlit.app   ← optional nav link
# • Redeploy after changing BACKEND_URL (rewrites are baked in at build time).
